{{Tesufɣeḍ-d deg ussan-a yezrin adlis icudden ɣer timerrit di Lwilaya n Tizi-Wezzu, acu i yesmedgen lebɣi dgem akken ad d‑yilli leqdic-agi ?}}
Aya yella-d deffir n tirza xedmeɣ ɣer kra n tmura tiberraniyin u nesɛi ara iferdisen n timerrit am wakka tekseb tmurt-nneɣ, yernu gan ccan i kra-nni yesɛan akken. Anect-a yuɣal-iyi d acqirrew akken ad rreɣ azal i yigarujen tekseb tamnaḍt n tmurt n Leqbayel deg uḥric-agi yesɛan azal muqren ama deg ugni n tdamsa neɣ n yidles neɣ n ttrebga. Rnu ɣef aya meṛṛa
