{{Tuɣal leɛnaya ɣef yismilen icudden ɣer timerrit?}}
Yesḥisif wul mi ara iwali amek ttuhamlen yesmilen tekseb tmurt n Leqbayel. Yettendaf wul mi ara iwali ismilen yeqqnen ɣer umezruy‑nneɣ, d yidles‑nneɣ d timadit‑nneɣ raɛen mebɣir leqrar , ur yelli win yečča wul-is ad d‑yini abbuh ! Amedya ɣef anect-a d taddart Nat Lqayed deg Iwaḍiyen (Agni G Aɣran) yettuneḥsaben d tigemmi taɣelnawt yernu ur din telli fell-as teɛessat neɣ ameskan ara d‑yesneɛten azal n umdiq-nni. Akka diɣ i teḍra d « les gavue r
